    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_22_621-639",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "621-639",
      "markText": "只有当一切结束了，你才会开始想念他。",
      "totalCount": 3258,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=621&rangeEnd=639",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=621&rangeEnd=639"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_25_4986-5045",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "4986-5045",
      "markText": "她抬起那张苍白的脸，茫茫然地，像一只走投无路的动物。她的眼中既没有爱意，也没有流露出惜别之情，她仿佛在望着一个陌生人。",
      "totalCount": 2288,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=4986&rangeEnd=5045",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=4986&rangeEnd=5045"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_21_2493-2503",
      "chapterUid": 21,
      "range": "2493-2503",
      "markText": "整个爱尔兰都在下雪。",
      "totalCount": 1840,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2493&rangeEnd=2503",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=21&rangeStart=2493&rangeEnd=2503"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_25_4181-4232",
      "chapterUid": 25,
      "range": "4181-4232",
      "markText": "难道她不应该快乐吗？凭什么她就应该受苦？她有权利获得幸福。弗兰克会抱住她，把她搂在怀里。他会拯救她的。",
      "totalCount": 1692,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=25&rangeStart=4181&rangeEnd=4232",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=25&rangeStart=4181&rangeEnd=4232"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_22_7506-7524",
      "chapterUid": 22,
      "range": "7506-7524",
      "markText": "只有当一切结束了，你才会开始想念他。",
      "totalCount": 1674,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=22&rangeStart=7506&rangeEnd=7524",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=22&rangeStart=7506&rangeEnd=7524"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_23_625-718",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "625-718",
      "markText": "真正的冒险不会发生在 整天待在家里的人身上—— 我得去外面的世界。",
      "totalCount": 1568,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=625&rangeEnd=718",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=625&rangeEnd=718"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_32_8325-8407",
      "chapterUid": 32,
      "range": "8325-8407",
      "markText": "在黑暗中，他感觉不到她在身边，也听不见她的声音了。他等待了几分钟，仔细聆听着。他什么也听不见：黑夜一片寂静。他又听了听：仍是一片寂静。他知道，他的孤独已在此刻降临。",
      "totalCount": 1530,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=32&rangeStart=8325&rangeEnd=8407",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=32&rangeStart=8325&rangeEnd=8407"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_23_5887-5919",
      "chapterUid": 23,
      "range": "5887-5919",
      "markText": "人这一生中最幸福的时光无疑是学生时代，他愿意付出一切来换取青春。",
      "totalCount": 1344,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5887&rangeEnd=5919",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=23&rangeStart=5887&rangeEnd=5919"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_24_5860-5909",
      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "5860-5909",
      "markText": "抬头望向黑暗，我发现自己是一个被虚荣心驱使，又被虚荣心嘲弄的可怜虫，眼里不禁燃起痛苦和愤怒的火焰。",
      "totalCount": 1296,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=5860&rangeEnd=5909",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=5860&rangeEnd=5909"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_34_5248-5275",
      "chapterUid": 34,
      "range": "5248-5275",
      "markText": "尽管她知道丈夫能力有限，但她欣赏他作为男人的抽象价值。",
      "totalCount": 1206,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=34&rangeStart=5248&rangeEnd=5275",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=34&rangeStart=5248&rangeEnd=5275"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_28_6732-6749",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "6732-6749",
      "markText": "那一刻，她才想起自己期待的是什么。",
      "totalCount": 1139,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=6732&rangeEnd=6749",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=6732&rangeEnd=6749"
    },
    {
