      "chapterUid": 24,
      "range": "1841-1886",
      "markText": "除了偶尔打声招呼，我从未同她讲过话，但她的名字却像一道咒语，召唤着我身体里所有愚蠢的血液。",
      "totalCount": 1134,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300095647&chapterUid=24&rangeStart=1841&rangeEnd=1886",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/be5328e0813ab8bdcg0179fb?chapterUid=24&rangeStart=1841&rangeEnd=1886"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300095647_40_14227-14289",
